<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/4" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="close-credits" style="height:2em;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>标题：</strong>SCP-2064-JP - 虫声<br />
<strong>作者：</strong>©︎<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/indonootoko" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3461191); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3461191&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609147214" alt="indonootoko" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3461191)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/indonootoko" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3461191); return false;">indonootoko</a></span>、<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mc-shrimp" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3691434); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3691434&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609147214" alt="mC shrimp" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3691434)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mc-shrimp" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3691434); return false;">mC shrimp</a></span>、<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hyoroika09" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3406303); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3406303&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609147214" alt="hyoroika09" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3406303)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hyoroika09" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3406303); return false;">hyoroika09</a></span><br />
<strong>译者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/backlight-sh" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5374263); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5374263&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609147214" alt="Backlight SH" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5374263)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/backlight-sh" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5374263); return false;">Backlight SH</a></span><br />
<strong>校订：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/snoj" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3266034); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3266034&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609147214" alt="snoj" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3266034)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/snoj" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3266034); return false;">snoj</a></span><br />
